    "In addition, the panel analyses in Section 3 confirm that adopters of different initiatives followed similar labor market trajectories prior to the arrival of AI chatbots.",
    "Second, because our data come from workers rather than senior leadership, our estimates reflect initiatives as perceived by workers."
